    "originContent": "*Press Ctrl+Option, speak:* \"Fix the race condition in the checkout flow from issue #312.\"",
    "translatedContent": "*Drücken Sie Ctrl+Option, sprechen Sie:* \"Behebe das Race Condition im Checkout-Flow aus Issue #312.\""
  },
